# CBT API

- Validate all inputs with Zod.
- Return consistent JSON: `{ data }` or `{ error, message }`.
- Never put business logic in route handlers — delegate to `src/services/`.
- Hash passwords with bcrypt — never store plain text.
- Student exam code validation happens server-side in session service.
- Use repository layer for all Prisma queries.
